parameters.name: SEPARATOR
parameters.description: One or more characters that separate the fields in a single line of tekst

parameters.name: ENCLOSURE
parameters.description: Possibility to enclose a field value by a pair of strings to allow separator characters

parameters.name: INCL_FIELD_NAMES
parameters.description: Flag to indicate if the field names are included as first line

parameters.name: ENCODING
parameters.description: Encoding standard used to construct the file

parameters.name: CONTROLS
parameters.description: Controls to generate along with the output
